  <verse number="25" style="v" />Since I am confident about this, I know that I will remain and continue with you all, for your progress and joy in the faith.

  <verse number="26" style="v" />As a result, your glorying in Christ Jesus because of me will abound because of my presence again with you.

  <verse number="27" style="v" />Only conduct your lives in a manner worthy of the gospel of Christ. Do this so that, whether I come to see you or I am absent, I may hear about how you are standing firmly in one spirit. I wish to hear that you are with one soul striving together for the faith of the gospel.
